OL,3,CIn pictures: The North West celebrates
OL,4,CWorld Book Day
OL,6,FChildren can use their #1 book token
OL,7,Fto buy a book of their choice.
OL,9,FBooks available cater for beginning
OL,10,Freaders, early readers, fluent readers
OL,11,Fand independent readers.
OL,13,FChildren's laureate and novelist Frank
OL,14,FCottrell-Boyce told ITV News Granada
OL,15,FReports about the importance of
OL,16,Freading with children at an early age.
OL,18,FChildren's laureate Frank Cottrell-
OL,19,FBoyce said reading should start from
OL,20,Fan early age and should not just be
OL,21,Flimited to the classroom.
