OL,6,FHe said: "If your child arrives at
OL,7,Fschool, and their first experience of
OL,8,Fbooks is cuddled up under a duvet, on
OL,9,Fa couch, then that book connects them
OL,10,Fwith a happy time.
OL,12,F"If the child's first experience of a
OL,13,Fbook is in school where they are faced
OL,14,Fwith this alien object, then they are
OL,15,Fat a huge disadvantage."
